    <note>Wang(2) Yuxi [12857] See documentation for father-in-law Ju(4) Chang [12853]. Link based on chronology, generational name and Wang(2) Yucheng's [12857] authorship of Ju(4) Chang's funerary inscriptions. There is probably a kinship tie between these Wang and Wang(2) Mian's [1853] lineage (also seen as Shandong people and intermarried with the Ju(4) of Shandong). Text would indicate that Yuxi was deceased at the time of Ju(4) Chang's death and therefore is probably an elder brother of Wang(2) Yucheng.</note>
